Head: Cerebral congestion; hallucination of vision, hearing and touch
Inclination to turn in a circle
JAWS FIRMLY CLENCHED

name: Carboneum oxygenisatum
details: Herpes zoster, pemphigus, and trismus are produced by this drug. Coldness, SLEEPINESS, loss of consciousness are marked. Vertigo.
